@if (@ViewData["Sent"] != "sent")
{

    <div class="intro-block2">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-3">
                    <img class="img-responsive tpad" src="img/vol.png">
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-9">
                    <h1>Party In The Park <span class="text-muted qback">&raquo; We need your sponsorship!</span></h1>
                    <p class="lead">After the success of “Party in the Park” held in <a href='@Url.Action("year2014", "PITP")'>2014</a> the event’s organisers are planning an even bigger and better day out for 2016!</p>
                    <p>This is a great opportunity for your business to help support this great community based festival. Sponsorship would give your organisation a great platform to promote itself within the local community.</p>
                    <p>Your sponsorship can help build upon the achievements of last year’s event. With your support we want to deliver a great day out for all who attend Fordham Park on September 2014. We are making efforts to build a network of local businesses and organisations that are keen to profit from involvement in what we foresee as a prosperous annual event. This is a great chance for you to benefit from participation in an occasion that will be perceived over the coming years as a valuable community asset.</p>
                    <p>Sponsorship will ensure that your businesses name and logo will feature in any “Party in the Park” promotional literature. We will be producing flyers, posters and adverts in order to publicise the event, which is an opportunity for your business to advertise itself as an important member of the community. Aside from traditional media promotion the event will also be publicised on the internet. Our web site employs the latest ‘responsive web design’ techniques to ensure that our message is displayed appropriately across all devices. Sponsors will have their name, logo, description, and appropriate web link displayed on the site.</p>
                    <p>This is a great chance for your organisation to be promoted in New Cross, Deptford and beyond. We hope you take up this opportunity to work with us to establish an annual event to be cherished.</p>

</div>
            </div>            
        </div>
    </div>
}
